channel.title: 667 Client won't load: Help. (SOLVED!)
channel.description:
[IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/2qvxwcg.png[/img]
Disturbed 667 Client will NOT load; can anyone help me?
Things i've tried: Deleting Cache Trying on a different user Things I know: Has the right Server IP Worked before
Issue was: I restarted my router; it got me a new "computer IP" so I just had to update settings in Router Thanks!
